{"tid":2373172,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"佐敦疫區變死城｜ 翟威廉封鎖線下死守心血清酒店 留宿舖頭冇請全職：我打緊3份工做埋批發","createTime":"2021-01-20T09:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T07:43:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c4351a05e633cfeed24bb2f39953d6fd6fc537f4","tid":2373172,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:03:26.000Z","msg":"第四波疫情令佐敦淪為疫區，多條街道圍上封鎖線，變成死城一樣。廣東道的店舖也差不多全關，一片冷清，但有一間清酒店仍然死守，燈火通明地繼續營業。原來店主是港男出身的35歲TVB藝員翟威廉，舖頭是他的心血，去年在疫情下，用了50萬來開業。為了好好守住這盤生意，他「不撤不退」。<br />\n<br />\n「你話生意難做，咁全香港都係，冇辦法，大家睇下點捱過去！」他說。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_773787_0/%E4%BD%90%E6%95%A6%E7%96%AB%E5%8D%80%E8%AE%8A%E6%AD%BB%E5%9F%8E-%E7%BF%9F%E5%A8%81%E5%BB%89%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8B%E6%AD%BB%E5%AE%88%E5%BF%83%E8%A1%80%E6%B8%85%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97-%E7%95%99%E5%AE%BF%E8%88%96%E9%A0%AD%E5%86%87%E8%AB%8B%E5%85%A8%E8%81%B7-%E6%88%91%E6%89%93%E7%B7%8A3%E4%BB%BD%E5%B7%A5%E5%81%9A%E5%9F%8B%E6%89%B9%E7%99%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_773787_0%2F%25E4%25BD%2590%25E6%2595%25A6%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259F%258E-%25E7%25BF%259F%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%25BB%2589%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E7%25B7%259A%25E4%25B8%258B%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%25A1%2580%25E6%25B8%2585%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597-%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%25BF%25E8%2588%2596%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%2586%2587%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%2585%25A8%25E8%2581%25B7-%25E6%2588%2591%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25B7%258A3%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%259F%258B%25E6%2589%25B9%25E7%2599%25BC&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=5982c095\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_773787_0%2F%25E4%25BD%2590%25E6%2595%25A6%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%259F%258E-%25E7%25BF%259F%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%25BB%2589%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%258E%259